{"tid":1250451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對家有咩免費嘢，記得唔好同佢慳","createTime":"2019-06-22T05:40:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T06:02:39.000Z","uid":42364,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"372ac55fe4afa0bad8e5cc1374fe4060ed7c93bc","tid":1250451,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:40:21.000Z","msg":"有米輪米<br />\n大公文匯拎得幾多得幾多<br />\n樓下大堂擺係到既成疊拎返屋企墊下檯，過兩日拎去回收<br />\n記得啲廢老拎完唔會回收，好唔環保架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返工返學朝早有人派就問佢拎多幾份<br />\n話想幫手派畀啲同事同學<br />\n落車就畀啲企係火車站地鐵站收報紙既阿婆<br />\n佢地會祝你身體健康架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住你拎多一份，就少一個人受害"},{"pid":"f0e67163b7691796133c4e292f1010f555fc0f12","tid":1250451,"uid":249971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:43:39.000Z","msg":"ccTVB"},{"pid":"6125257158dd77f1770316d11738c94ff9f0a610","tid":1250451,"uid":39752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b55b96a049e74beff2b0206d8b8344a5cec4c0e","tid":1250451,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />消耗敵人資源"},{"pid":"2d46c460f06fb11c9f80912d74b143f392b63d0d","tid":1250451,"uid":90589,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:49:07.000Z","msg":"如果拎太撚多，等陣俾佢話係全港最受歡迎紙媒，發行量第一，最有公信力報章點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22edea97a32e3248fd73689502a770c08e7a18cc","tid":1250451,"uid":39360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d46c460f06fb11c9f80912d74b143f392b63d0d","tid":1250451,"uid":90589,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:49:07.000Z